'''小劳伦斯·约瑟夫·霍甘'''（Lawrence Joseph Hogan Jr.；{{bd|1956年|5月25日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物。拉里·霍甘自2015年開始擔任第62任馬里蘭州州長。拉里·霍甘的黨籍是[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/republican-larry-hogan-wins-md-governors-race-in-stunning-upset/2014/11/05/9eb8bf46-60ac-11e4-8b9e-2ccdac31a031_story.html?tid=pm_pop |title=Republican Larry Hogan wins Md. governor’s race in stunning upset |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=November 5, 2014 |date=November 5, 2014 |first1=John |last1=Wagner |first2=Jenna |last2=Johnson |archive-date=2019-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229200130/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/republican-larry-hogan-wins-md-governors-race-in-stunning-upset/2014/11/05/9eb8bf46-60ac-11e4-8b9e-2ccdac31a031_story.html?tid=pm_pop |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，拉里·霍甘宣布他將競選馬里蘭州州長，並順利當選<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kartalija|first1=Jessica|title=Larry Hogan: ‘Tonight, Real Change Has Come To Maryland’|url=http://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2014/11/04/larry-hogan-courts-last-minute-voters/|accessdate=November 5, 2014|work=[[WJZ-TV|CBS Baltimore]]|date=November 4, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105082959/http://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2014/11/04/larry-hogan-courts-last-minute-voters/|archive-date=2014-11-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

